node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Madison Beer on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: now these pages are very much so covered in tears….. i seriously had to write myself a letter a month ago because of how the thought of being nominated for a vma was making me feel. i was truly preparing to be let down and i thought hey man u don’t need to be sad if you don’t get one, lemme tell my future self that. i’ve never been nominated for anything ever really so this just didn’t even seem possible. i’m just really shocked and grateful and emotional right now & don’t really know what to say but please vote the link is on my story and thank you and yeah @mtv i love you so much . i’m bawling IM NOMINATED FOR A VMA 😭😭😭😭😭😭😭
